    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，IsPositive之后必须分支。我们用一个选择节点（choice）来做条件判断，两条分支：一条是n小于0走False，另一条是n等于0走True。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IsPositive",
        "if_state",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下：从IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode指向IsPositive，IsPositive再连到选择节点if_state，然后if_state分出两条带条件标注的线——一条标\"if n < 0\"到False，另一条标\"if n = 0\"到True。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IsPositive",
        "if_state",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，条件标注有点问题。n等于0应该不算正数吧？这里True分支的逻辑是n大于0才对，但图上写的是n=0。我们需要把条件改成\"if n 0\"走True。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "True",
        "if_state"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确实，n=0既不是正数也不是负数。不过您刚才说的是n大于0走True，但图上目前标的是n=0。我需要确认一下：最终版本是保留n=0到True，还是改成n0到True？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "True",
        "if_state"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按实际业务需求，这个IsPositive只关心严格正数，所以n=0应该归到False那边。我们调整一下：if_state到True的条件是n0，到False的条件包含n<0和n=0两种情况。不过为了图简洁，False只标n<0，业务上默认非正数都走这边。",
      "elements_involved": [
